Class LandCards

  • java.lang.Object
    • game.Cards
      • game.LandCards
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CapCompany, PropertyCard, RailroadCard, UtilityCard

    public class LandCards
extends Cards
    The abstract landCards class for representing the cards of lands with some specific instances. Instances of card is getting from txt document only the current rent is changing during game.

    • Constructor Detail

      • LandCards

        public LandCards(java.lang.String CardName,
         java.lang.String color,
         int landPrice,
         int rent0,
         int rent1,
         int rent2,
         int rent3,
         int rent4,
         int rent5,
         int rent6,
         int buildingPrice,
         int mortgagedPrice)
        The default constructor of the landCards class. sets currentRent to rent0 which means the rent without any building or any majority. sets landPrice and color information taking from the txt document. sets landOwner null for all lands initially. sets isSold false for all lands initially. sets all rents information taking from the txt document for each condition. sets mortgagedPrice and building price information taking from the txt document. sets isMortgaged false for all lands initially.
        Parameters:
        CardName - The name of the land
        color - The color of the land
        landPrice - The price of the land for buying
        rent0 - The rent of the land without any buildings and majorities
        rent1 - The rent of the land with 1 house
        rent2 - The rent of the land with 2 houses
        rent3 - The rent of the land with 3 houses
        rent4 - The rent of the land with 4 houses
        rent5 - The rent of the land with hotel
        rent6 - The rent of the land with skyscraper
        buildingPrice - The price for putting a building on the land
        mortgagePrice - The price that you will take when mortgage the land
